% Statics of linear λ-calculus
%======================================================%

LF oft : lctx _ → obj → tp → type =
| oft/var : upd Δ _ X X A A 𝟙 𝟘 Δ' → exh Δ' → oft Δ X A
| oft/lam : ({x:obj} oft (cons Δ x A 𝟙) (M x) B)
	→ oft Δ (lam M) (A -o B)
| oft/app : oft Δ₁ M (A -o B) → oft Δ₂ N A → merge Δ₁ Δ₂ Δ
	→ oft Δ (app M N) B;